'''1961年大西洋飓风季'''于6月15日正式开始，同年11月15日结束<ref name="fmn">{{cite news|newspaper=Florence Morning News|title=Hurricane Season Here Today|year=1961}}</ref><ref name="upi1">{{cite news|agency = United Press International | year = 1961 | title = Hurricane "season" at end}}</ref>，通常情况下每年[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]的绝大多数[[热带气旋|热带]]或[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]都是在这段时间形成。本季形成的大型飓风数量创下新纪录，直到44年后才被[[2005年大西洋飓风季|追平]]<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A3.html | title = What is a super-typhoon? What is a major hurricane ? What is an intense hurricane? | author = Stan Goldberg | work = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory; [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | date =  | archive-date = 2016-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160927101821/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A3.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ACE">{{cite report | work = Hurricane Research Division; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-03 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051842/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html }}</ref>。按热带风暴数量计算，飓风季的活跃程度超过平均水平，共有11场获命名的风暴。[[1961年飓风安娜|飓风安娜]]于7月20日在[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]附近的东[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]发展形成，是本季首场风暴。气旋对向风群岛构成轻度破坏，然后又以飓风强度袭击[[伯利兹|英属洪都拉斯]]（今[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]），再在[[中美洲|中美洲]]产生大风并引发洪灾。安娜一共导致一人死亡，经济损失约为30万美元{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有损失数额均换算成1961年[[美元|美元]]。|group="注"}}。接下来一个半月，大西洋的热带天气活动陷入沉寂，直至飓风贝特西于9月2日成型。贝特西的最高强度达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]的四级飓风标准，但自始至终位于海上，所以没有对陆地造成影响。

[[飓风卡拉|飓风卡拉]]是本季影响最大的风暴之一，达到[[五级大西洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]强度后仅有小幅减弱就直接袭击[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]，造成43人丧生，损失总额约为3亿2574万美元。[[1961年飓风黛比|飓风黛比]]最高达到三级飓风标准，主要在东太平洋活动。气旋存在早期令[[佛得角|佛得角]]天气恶劣，致使一架飞机坠毁，共60人死亡。接下来，黛比又以一级飓风强度（有可能已转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]）吹袭[[爱尔兰岛|爱尔兰岛]]。[[飓风埃丝特|飓风埃丝特]]是本季形成的下一场风暴，一度威胁以大型飓风强度袭击[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]，但实际上却快速弱化，[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]时已降级成热带风暴。气旋产生的总体影响很小，经济损失约为600万美元，但因造成[[美国海军|美国海军]]飞机失事而引起七人遇难。此后，无名热带风暴和飓风弗朗西丝都只对陆地构成轻微影响。10月中旬，热带风暴格尔达又在[[牙买加|牙买加]]和[[古巴|古巴]]东部引发洪灾，致使12人丧生。

[[飓风哈蒂|飓风哈蒂]]是本季强度最高的风暴，在飓风季后期形成并在达到五级标准后袭击伯利兹。哈蒂经确认共导致319人丧生，损失数额约6030万美元。由于伯利兹市所受破坏太过严重，首府不得不迁至内陆的[[贝尔墨邦|贝尔墨邦]]。风暴残留之后还可能在东太平洋促成[[1961年太平洋飓风季#热带风暴西蒙娜|热带风暴西蒙娜]]。11月初，有热带低气压在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]降下小雨，之后又增强成飓风珍妮。热带风暴英加是本季最后一场风暴，但没有对陆地产生影响，于11月8日消散。9月11日，大西洋盆地上空有贝特西、卡拉和黛比三场飓风同时存在，是[[1893年大西洋飓风季|1893年]]后首次出现这种情况，下一次则是超过三分之一个世纪之后的[[1998年大西洋飓风季|1998年]]。总体而计，1961年大西洋飓风季的所有热带气旋共导致348人遇难，损失总额约3亿9100万美元。

== 季节总览 ==
1961年大西洋飓风季于6月15日正式开始<ref name="fmn" />，活跃程度超过平均水平，共形成11场热带风暴，超出[[1950年大西洋飓风季|1950]]至2000年间平均每季9.6场命名风暴的平均值<ref name="Gray Dec">{{cite report |author1=Philip J. Klotzbach |author2=William M. Gray |date=2006-12-08 |title=Extended Range Forecast of Atlantic Seasonal Hurricane Activity and U.S. Landfall Strike Probability for 2007 |publisher=Colorado State University |accessdate=2014-03-28 |url=http://hurricane.atmos.colostate.edu/forecasts/2006/dec2006/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304001001/http://hurricane.atmos.colostate.edu/forecasts/2006/dec2006/ |archivedate=2016-03-04 |deadurl=yes |location=Boulder, Colorado }}</ref>。共有八场风暴达到飓风强度<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author1 = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | archivedate = 2016-04-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411090349/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt }}</ref>，同样高于1950至2000年间5.9场飓风的平均值<ref name="Gray Dec" />。同时，还有七场飓风达到大型飓风标准<ref name="HURDAT" />，创下新纪录，直至2005年才被[[2005年大西洋飓风季|追平]]<ref name="ACE" />。此外，本季还有两场大型飓风达到[[五级大西洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]强度，全季共有四场飓风和两场热带风暴[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref name="HURDAT" />，一共夺走348条人命，经济损失总额达3亿9160万美元<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201458/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1961.pdf | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1961.pdf | title = The Hurricane Season of 1961 | deadurl = no | author = Gordon E. Dunn | date = 1962-03 | work = [[美国国家气象局|United States Weather Bureau]] | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | location = Miami, Florida }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | volume = 3 | issue = 9 | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-9FF6F836-52BD-4912-9F1F-2C5B28F9E210.pdf | title = Storm Data And Unusual Weather Phenomena: September 1961 | author = Luther Hodges | date = 1961-09 | work = [[美国商务部|United States Department of Commerce]] | pages = 99–101, 103 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-02-01 | format = PDF | location = Asheville, North Carolina | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201051314/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-9FF6F836-52BD-4912-9F1F-2C5B28F9E210.pdf | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | volume = 3 | issue = 12 | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-52F4B7BD-1C8E-49D5-8E58-2306A1702BBA.pdf | title = Storm Data and Unusual Weather Phenomena: December 1961 | author = Luther Hodges | work = United States Department of Commerce | page = 120 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Asheville, North Carolina | accessdate = 2014-02-03 | date = 1961-11 | deadurl = yes | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140203173717/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-52F4B7BD-1C8E-49D5-8E58-2306A1702BBA.pdf | archivedate = 2014-02-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | doi = 10.5772/54039 | author1 = Kieran R. Hickey | author2 = Christina Connolly-Johnston | publisher = InTech | year = 2012 | isbn = 978-953-51-0867-2 | pages = 183–198 | chapter = The Impact of Hurricane Debbie (1961) and Hurricane Charley (1986) on Ireland | title = Advances in Hurricane Research — Modelling, Meteorology, Preparedness and Impacts | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160604040541/http://www.intechopen.com/books/advances-in-hurricane-research-modelling-meteorology-preparedness-and-impacts/the-impact-of-hurricane-debbie-1961-and-hurricane-charley-1986-on-ireland | url = http://www.intechopen.com/books/advances-in-hurricane-research-modelling-meteorology-preparedness-and-impacts/the-impact-of-hurricane-debbie-1961-and-hurricane-charley-1986-on-ireland | archivedate = 2016-06-04 }}</ref><ref name="ii">{{cite news | newspaper = Irish Independent | date = 1961-09-18 | title = Gale Killed Fifteen | page = 3}} {{subscription required | via = Irish Newspaper Archives}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | publisher = Met éireann | year = 2012 | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003951/http://www.met.ie/climate-ireland/weather-events/Sep1961_hurricane-Debbie.pdf | url = http://www.met.ie/climate-ireland/weather-events/Sep1961_hurricane-Debbie.pdf | format = PDF | title = Exceptional Weather Events - "Hurricane Debbie" | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = yes | date =  }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120204203444/http://www.ss346.com/PDFs/ImhofRescue1961.pdf | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-02-04 | url = http://www.ss346.com/PDFs/ImhofRescue1961.pdf | format = PDF | title = Rescue at Sea | accessdate = 2012-02-04 | author = Patrick J. Imhof | pages = 4-6 | date = 2005-09-13 | location = Pensacola, Florida }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/gerda/news/savannah.gif | title = Floods Fatal To 5 Jamaicans | date = 1961-10-20 | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = Savannah Morning News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043010/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/gerda/news/savannah.gif | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | location = Kingston, Jamaica | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | deadurl = no | page = 5 }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release | title = Belize Marked 45th Anniversary of Deadly Hurricane Hattie | url = http://www.nemo.org.bz/cgi-bin/nemonews/exec/view.cgi?archive=1&num=285 | work = Belize National Emergency Management Organization (NEMO) | accessdate = 2012-07-23 | publisher = NEMO Press Officer | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120723114312/http://www.nemo.org.bz/cgi-bin/nemonews/exec/view.cgi?archive=1&num=285 | archivedate = 2012-07-23 | date = 2006-11-02 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。[[1961年飓风黛比|飓风黛比]]虽然远离海岸，但存在早期及转变成温带气旋后依然引起人员伤亡和破坏<ref name="IT">{{cite book | doi = 10.5772/54039 | author = Kieran R. Hickey | author2 = Christina Connolly-Johnston | publisher = InTech | year = 2012 | isbn = 978-953-51-0867-2 | pages = 183–198 | chapter = The Impact of Hurricane Debbie (1961) and Hurricane Charley (1986) on Ireland | title = Advances in Hurricane Research — Modelling, Meteorology, Preparedness and Impacts | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160604040541/http://www.intechopen.com/books/advances-in-hurricane-research-modelling-meteorology-preparedness-and-impacts/the-impact-of-hurricane-debbie-1961-and-hurricane-charley-1986-on-ireland | url = http://www.intechopen.com/books/advances-in-hurricane-research-modelling-meteorology-preparedness-and-impacts/the-impact-of-hurricane-debbie-1961-and-hurricane-charley-1986-on-ireland | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | archivedate = 2016-06-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="ii" /><ref name="metie">{{cite report | publisher = Met éireann | year = 2012 | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | title = Exceptional Weather Events - "Hurricane Debbie" | url = http://www.met.ie/climate-ireland/weather-events/Sep1961_hurricane-Debbie.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003951/http://www.met.ie/climate-ireland/weather-events/Sep1961_hurricane-Debbie.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>。

虽然飓风季早在6月15日就已正式开始<ref name="fmn" />，但[[1961年飓风安娜|飓风安娜]]作为首场风暴直至7月20日才发展成型。7月24日安娜消散后，大西洋盆地的热带天气活动再度陷入沉寂，整个8月都没有热带气旋形成，直到9月2日才发展出飓风贝特西。接下来飓风季转向喧嚣，四天内就有两场大型飓风形成，分别是飓风卡拉和黛比。9月11日，大西洋盆地上空有贝特西、卡拉和黛比三场飓风同时存在<ref name="HURDAT" />，是1893年后首次出现这种情况，下一次则是超过三分之一个世纪之后的1998年<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E18.html | title = Subject: E18) What was the largest number of hurricanes in the Atlantic Ocean at the same time? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160429011729/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E18.html | author = Christopher W. Landsea | work = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-04-29 | date =  }}</ref>。埃丝特虽在9月10日就已成形，但直到同月12日才达到飓风强度。12日晚，又有热带风暴在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]上空形成，气旋总体沿[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]移动，但持续时间很短，气象机构也没有为其命名。<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="unnamed">{{cite report | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/090/mwr-090-08-0351.pdf | title = Northbound Tropical Cyclone | author = Richard Fay | date = 1962-08 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = United States Weather Bureau | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040058/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/090/mwr-090-08-0351.pdf | deadurl = no }}</ref>

9月26日，黛比转变成温带气旋，飓风弗朗西斯则在四天后形成。进入10月后，大西洋盆地上空的热带天气活动显著减少，这个月只形成两场风暴，分别是热带风暴格尔达和[[飓风海蒂|飓风海蒂]]。海蒂是本季最强烈的热带气旋，[[最大持续风速|最大风力时速]]达260公里，最低[[气压|气压]]仅920[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）。经过小幅弱化，飓风于10月31日袭击[[伯利兹|英属洪都拉斯]]，最终于11月1日逐渐消散。当晚，飓风珍妮在[[安地卡岛|安地卡岛]]附近发展形成，其强度一直不高，最终于11月8日转变成温带气旋。热带风暴英加是本季最后一场风暴，于11月5日在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]形成，再于三天后消散，<ref name="HURDAT" />此时离飓风季正式结束还有一星期时间<ref name="upi1" />。

本季的活跃程度也通过累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，达到205，是有纪录以来最高的大西洋飓风季之一<ref name="ACE" />。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高，持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高。只有在热带气旋风速达到或超过每小时63公里（34[[节_(单位)|节]]）或热带风暴强度时才会计算该指数，并纳入全面的气象公告。此外，正式统计中不会计算[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的数值。<ref>{{cite report |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |work=National Climatic Data Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2016-06-08 |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>

