7月20日，一股朝东面移动的[[东风波|东风波]]在[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]附近发展成热带风暴安娜<ref name="MWR">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1961.pdf | title = The Hurricane Season of 1961 | author = Gordon E. Dunn | date = 1962-03 | work = United States Weather Bureau | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201458/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1961.pdf | deadurl = no | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref><ref name="HURDAT" />。风暴向西穿越[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]，因外界环境有利而于当晚达到飓风强度。次日清晨，气旋达到二级飓风标准，并且继续强化，于当晚成为本季首场大型飓风。7月22日达到最高强度后，安娜在掠过[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]北岸期间略有减弱。风暴此后继续弱化，于7月24日以持续风速每小时130公里强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]英属洪都拉斯。飓风在陆地上空急剧减弱，于当晚完全消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

成为热带气旋并在背风群岛上空发展期间，安娜给[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]带去狂风，不过当地只有少数农作物、树木和电线杆受损<ref name="tg">{{cite news | newspaper = The Daily Gleaner | date = 1961-07 | title = Anna Should Miss Jamaica}}</ref>。另有多个岛上出现强风，但没有遭受破坏。行经[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]以北洋面时，风暴在该国产生强风，最高风速达到每小时115公里。<ref name="nhca">{{cite report | title = Report on Hurricane Anna - July 20, 1961 | author = Ralph L. Higgs | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshsju02.gif | date = 1961-08-04 | work = U.S. Weather Bureau Office San Juan, Puerto Rico | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | pages = 2 | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | location = San Juan, Puerto Rico | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034330/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshsju02.gif | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>洪都拉斯北部因狂风受到大面积破坏，该国有至少36户民居被毁，另有228户受损<ref name="pshmhtg">{{cite report | title = Report on Hurricane Anna | author = Etat; Gordon E. Dunn | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303174042/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshmhtg.gif | date = 1961-08-04 | work = U.S. Weather Bureau Office Miami, Florida | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | page = 11 | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | location = Miami, Florida | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/preloc/pshmhtg.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。[[格拉西亚斯-阿迪奥斯省|格拉西亚斯-阿迪奥斯省]]受到气旋重创，数以百计的居民无家可归<ref name="mgp">{{cite news | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; National Hurricane Center | date = 1961-07 | title = Miami Gets Pelted With Short Storms | accessdate = 2016-04-10 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193805/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/news/miami.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/anna/news/miami.gif | deadurl = no }}</ref>，另外还有约5000棵椰子树被强风推倒<ref name="pshmhtg" />。整场飓风一共造成一人死亡，经济损失约为30万美元，其中大部分发生在中美洲<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="mgp" />。
