9月3日，西南加勒比海的热带辐合带内有狂风天气发展成热带低气压<ref name="new12">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092109/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/new12.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/new12.gif | title = Carla Preliminary Report | author = ECH | date = 1961-09-21 | work = United States Weather Bureau | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | page = 12 | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。气旋在朝西北行进期间缓慢增强，到9月5日时已强化成热带风暴并获名“卡拉”（{{lang|en|Carla}}）<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="new13">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/new13.gif | title = Carla Preliminary Report | author = ECH | date = 1961-09-21 | work = United States Weather Bureau | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | page = 13 | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214413/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/new13.gif | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>，再于约24小时后升级成飓风<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="new14">{{cite report | title = Carla Preliminary Report | author = ECH | date = 1961-09-21 | work = United States Weather Bureau | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | page = 14 | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | format = GIF | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065757/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/new14.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/new14.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。不久后，风暴蜿蜒北上逼近[[尤卡坦海峡|尤卡坦海峡]]。9月7日晚，卡拉进入墨西哥湾并从[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]东北近海掠过。次日清晨，气旋已成为大型飓风。风暴恢复西北走势并继续增强，于9月11日达到[[五级大西洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]标准。当夜，卡拉略有减弱，但规模依旧庞大，以持续风速每小时233公里强度从[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[卡尔霍恩县_(得克萨斯州)|卡尔霍恩县]][[奥康纳港_(德克萨斯州)|奥康纳港]]（{{lang|en|Port O'Connor}}）附近登陆。进入陆地上空后，风暴快速弱化，于9月12日降级成热带风暴。卡拉总体保持北上趋势，于9月13日中心位于[[俄克拉何马州|俄克拉何马州]]南部上空时转变成温带气旋。系统残留继续向东北移动，于9月14日进入[[加拿大|加拿大]]上空，最终于9月16日清晨在[[契德利角|契德利角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Chidley}}）附近逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

穿越尤卡坦海峡期间，卡拉的外围[[雨带|雨带]]在[[古巴|古巴]]和尤卡坦半岛产生狂风并引发严重的局部洪灾，但没有出现由此造成破坏或人员伤亡的报道<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="google72">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Whips Cuba; Winds Batter Key West | page = 72 | date = 1961-09-07 | newspaper = The Miami News}}</ref>。[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]起初认为飓风对[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]构成重大威胁<ref>{{cite report | title = Hurricane Advisory Number 15 Carla | author = Conner | date = 1961-09-07 | work = Weather Bureau Office New Orleans, Louisiana | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | archivedate = 2013-06-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130618091759/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/public/tcp0710z.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/public/tcp0710z.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>，但风暴实际在该州产生的风速不强，降雨量不超过80毫米<ref name="google72" />。相比之下，德克萨斯州[[拉瓦卡港_(德克萨斯州)|拉瓦卡港]]测得的阵风时速高达270公里，气旋还在该州催生出多场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]并构成重大影响，其中最具破坏性的一场导致八人死亡，55人受伤，约200幢建筑物严重受损，其中至少60幢毁于一旦<ref name="pshaus1">{{cite report | title = Hurricane Carla in Texas September 8 to 13th, 1961 | author = Robert Orton | date = 1961-09-16 | work = Weather Bureau Office Galveston, Texas | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | page = 1 | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | archivedate = 2013-06-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130618091357/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/pshaus1.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/pshaus1.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。整个德克萨斯州共有1915套民居、568套农业建筑和415套其它建筑被毁，另有5万零723户民宅、5620套农业建筑和1万零487套其它建筑受损，该州共有34人丧生，损失总额至少有三亿美元。[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]同样有多场龙卷风着陆，引起140套民房、11座农场和其它部分建筑被毁，另有231套住房、11座农场和其它部分建筑受到重创，748套民居、75座农场及其它部分建筑受到轻到中度破坏<ref>{{cite report | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304024148/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/pshaus.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/preloc/pshaus.gif | title = List of known dead in Texas from Hurricane Carla as of September 18th | author = Robert Orton | date = 1961-09-18 | work = Weather Bureau Office Galveston, Texas | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。受卡拉影响，路易斯安那州共有六人死亡，经济损失总额约2500万美元<ref name="tcr2">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/prenhc/prelim2.gif | title = Hurricane Carla: September 4–14, 1961 (A Preliminary Report) | date = 1961-09-18 | work = United States Weather Bureau | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130618091844/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1961/carla/prenhc/prelim2.gif | publisher = National Hurricane Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | page = 2 | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2013-06-18 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。风暴还在另外多个州降下暴雨，其中又以[[堪萨斯州|堪萨斯州]]情况严重<ref name="tcmidwest">{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050336/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidwest.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmidwest.html | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall for the Midwest | date = 2013 | publisher = Weather Prediction Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | location = College Park, Maryland }}</ref>，该州有五人死于山洪爆发，农作物也受到重大破坏<ref name="stormdata961">{{cite journal | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-9FF6F836-52BD-4912-9F1F-2C5B28F9E210.pdf | title = Storm Data And Unusual Weather Phenomena: September 1961 | author = Luther Hodges | date = 1961-09 | work = United States Department of Commerce | pages = 99–101, 103 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-02-01 | format = PDF | location = Asheville, North Carolina | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201051314/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-9FF6F836-52BD-4912-9F1F-2C5B28F9E210.pdf | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | volume = 3 | issue = 9 }}</ref>。整场飓风一共导致46人遇难，损失总额达3亿2574万美元<ref name="tcr2" /><ref name="stormdata961" /><ref name="stormdata1261">{{cite journal | title = Storm Data and Unusual Weather Phenomena: December 1961 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140203173717/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-52F4B7BD-1C8E-49D5-8E58-2306A1702BBA.pdf | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-52F4B7BD-1C8E-49D5-8E58-2306A1702BBA.pdf | author = Luther Hodges | work = United States Department of Commerce | page = 120 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center; National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Asheville, North Carolina | accessdate = 2014-02-03 | format = PDF | archivedate = 2014-02-03 | volume = 3 | issue = 12 | date = 1961-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。卡拉的残留还在加拿大安大略和新不伦瑞克产生强风，但造成的影响基本局限于停电、树枝断裂及树木倒塌<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215055/http://www.ec.gc.ca/hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=9D9BF402-1 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=9D9BF402-1 | title = 1961-Carla | date = 2009-11-05 | publisher = Environment Canada | accessdate = 2016-06-08 | location = Fredericton, New Brunswick | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。
