{{main|1961年飓风黛比}}
8月下旬，中非上空出现[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]<ref name="Precursor">{{cite report | author = C. O. Erickson | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 1963-02 | accessdate = 2016-06-09 | title = An Incipient Hurricane Near The West African Coast | format = PDF | pages = 61–68 | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/091/mwr-091-02-0061.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131112035152/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/091/mwr-091-02-0061.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-11-12 | location = Miami, Florida }}</ref>，估计于9月6日发展成热带风暴。当晚，黛比以强烈热带风暴或是飓风的最低标准强度从[[佛得角|佛得角]]南部经过<ref name="HURDAT" />，致使一架飞机坠毁，共60人死亡<ref name="metie" />。离开佛得角群岛后，气象机构在之后几天里都因缺乏数据而难以确定风暴的具体位置和强度，只知气旋是在朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动一段时间后转向北上，直至9月10日有商业航班接触风暴后才确定其位置<ref name="Prelim">{{cite report | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/hurricanes/Qc9452d393h81961.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304044227/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/hurricanes/Qc9452d393h81961.pdf | deadurl = no | title = Hurricane Debbie — September 7–15, 1961 Preliminary Report | year = 1961 | work = National Weather Bureau | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-06-09 | location = Miami, Florida | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>。次日，黛比经过强化达到风力时速190公里的最高强度，已是三级飓风。接下来气旋逐渐减弱，前进速度也渐渐放缓。<ref name="HURDAT" />到了9月13日，黛比因受到[[西风带|西风带]]影响而开始向东北偏东方向加速行进<ref name="Prelim" />。

9月15日，系统以飓风最低标准强度从[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]西部上空经过<ref name="HURDAT" />，但气象部门无法确定风暴这时仍属热带气旋还是已转变成温带气旋。接下来黛比在逼近不列颠群岛的过程中得以强化<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="Prelim" />，于9月16日在西爱尔兰海岸掠过。不久后，系统经确认已转变成温带气旋并继续向东北进发<ref name="HURDAT" />。爱尔兰岛大部分地区的风速创下新纪录，近海测得时速183公里的最强阵风<ref name="CS1">{{cite news | newspaper = Connacht Sentinel | date = 1961-09-19 | title = Repairing Hurricane Damage | page = 10}} {{subscription required | via = Irish Newspaper Archives}}</ref>。狂风造成大范围破坏和干扰，刮倒数以万计的树木，还有大量供电线缆中断<ref name="AC1">{{cite news | newspaper = Anglo-Celt | date = 1961-09-23 | title = Storm Reports From The Areas | page = 9}} {{subscription required | via = Irish Newspaper Archives}}</ref><ref name="UH1">{{cite news | newspaper = Ulster Herald | date = 1961-09-23 | title = The Storm Made Much Work | page = 7}} {{subscription required | via = Irish Newspaper Archives}}</ref>。不计其数的建筑物遭受到不同程度损伤，许多较小的建筑物被毁<ref name="JSTOR">{{cite journal | journal = The Irish Naturalists' Journal | author1 = J. G. Gruickshank | author2 = N. Stephens | author3 = L. J. Symons | date = 1962-01 | volume = 14 | issue = 1 | pages = 4–12 | title = Report of the Hurricane in Ireland on Saturday, 16 September, 1961 | jstor = 25534822}}</ref>。大面积的大麦、玉米和小麦作物毁于一旦<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Irish Farmers Journal | title = Crop Losses | date = 1961-09-23 | page = 1}} {{subscription required | via = Irish Newspaper Archives}}</ref>。整个爱尔兰岛共有18人丧生，其中[[爱尔兰共和国|爱尔兰共和国]]12人，[[北爱尔兰|北爱尔兰]]六人<ref name="IT" /><ref name="ii" />。爱尔兰共和国遭受的经济损失约为4000到5000万美元，北爱尔兰也有至少400万美元<ref name="IT" />。大不列颠岛部分地区同样受到时速超过160公里的狂风摧残<ref name="MWR" />。
