10月下旬，西加勒比海连续数日有[[低气压|低气压区]]存在<ref name="HattiePrelim">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234952/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/hurricanes/Qc9452h39h81961.pdf | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/hurricanes/Qc9452h39h81961.pdf | title = Hurricane Esther — October 27–31, 1961 Preliminary Report | year = 1961 | work = National Weather Bureau | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | page = 4 | accessdate = 2016-06-09 | location = Miami, Florida | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。10月27日，[[圣安德列斯-普罗维登西亚和圣卡塔利娜群岛省|圣安德列斯群岛]]的机场及海上一艘船只发现低气压区内有闭合环流中心存在<ref name="MWR" />，美国国家飓风中心因此从10月27日将系统归类成热带风暴，并以“哈蒂”（{{lang|en|Hattie}}）为其命名。风暴朝北面和东北偏北前进，很快就达到飓风标准，次日又成为大型飓风。接下来风暴在牙买加以西海域转向西进并增强至五级飓风标准，风力时速达到260公里，再在减弱成四级飓风后从[[伯利兹市|伯利兹市]]南部登陆。气旋继续向西南进发，在中美洲的山区地形上空快速弱化，于11月1日逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />风暴残留此后有可能还在东太平洋促成热带风暴西蒙娜<ref name="MWR" />。

哈蒂首先对加勒比地区西南部产生影响，圣安德列斯岛有一人死亡，风速达到飓风强度<ref name="MWR" />。气象机构起初预测风暴会继续北上袭击古巴，岛上因此疏散人员<ref>{{cite news | title = 'Cane Hattie Threatens Western Cuba, Florida | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Palm Beach Post | page = 1 | location = Miami, Florida | date = 1961-10-30}}</ref>。但哈蒂实际上向西转向，古巴因此幸免，[[大开曼|大开曼]]降下290毫米雨量<ref name="HattiePrelim" />。英属洪都拉斯受灾最为严重，首府伯利兹市受到狂风巨浪和强烈的风暴潮重创。据领地总督估算，全城有约70%的建筑受损，导致上万居民流离失所。<ref name="upi112">{{cite news | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | date = 1961-11-02 | title = Hattie's Toll is 62: Martial Law Declared | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | pages = 1A, 2A | location = Belize City, British Honduras | accessdate = 2016-06-09 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=204nAAAAIBAJ&sjid=JHkDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hattie&pg=5523%2C397222 | archive-date = 2020-12-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201211020439/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=204nAAAAIBAJ&sjid=JHkDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hattie&pg=5523,397222 | dead-url = no }}</ref>由于灾情太重，首府不得不迁往内陆的[[贝尔墨邦|贝尔墨邦]]<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Sarasota Herald-Tribune | date = 1971-09-07 | title = Hurricane 'Edith' Deepens Rapidly | agency = Associated Press | pages = 1A, 4A | accessdate = 2016-06-09 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HjogAAAAIBAJ&sjid=c2YEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7339,2936965&dq=hurricane+hattie&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-12-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201211020416/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HjogAAAAIBAJ&sjid=c2YEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7339%2C2936965&dq=hurricane+hattie&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。整场飓风一共在英属洪都拉斯造成307人丧生，经济损失约6000万美元<ref name="MWR" /><ref>{{cite press release | title = Belize Marked 45th Anniversary of Deadly Hurricane Hattie | archivedate = 2012-07-23 | date = 2006-11-02 | url = http://www.nemo.org.bz/cgi-bin/nemonews/exec/view.cgi?archive=1&num=285 | work = Belize National Emergency Management Organization (NEMO) | accessdate = 2012-07-23 | publisher = NEMO Press Officer | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120723114312/http://www.nemo.org.bz/cgi-bin/nemonews/exec/view.cgi?archive=1&num=285 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。据政府估算，哈蒂的破坏程度比夺走2000余条人命的[[1931年伯利兹飓风|1931年伯利兹飓风]]要高得多，幸得事先获得警告才大幅降低死亡人数。此外，飓风还在[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]导致11人丧生，洪都拉斯也有一人遇难。<ref name="MWR" />
