=== 其它风暴 ===
根据墨西哥的报道，[[塔巴斯科州|塔巴斯科州]]和[[夸察夸尔科斯|夸察夸尔科斯]]西岸近海在6月底有热带低气压形成，[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]]北部受到气旋的严重影响，于6月30日降下暴雨<ref name="vera">{{cite report | journal = Inundaciones 2005 en el Estado de Veracruz | title = Riesgo Quimico Asociado a Fenominos Hidrometeorologicos en el Estado de Verzacruz | author1 = Humberto Bravo Alavarez | author2 = Rodolfo Sosa Echeverria | author3 = Pablo Sanchez Alavarez | author4 = Arturo Butron Silva | page = 317 | date = 2006-06-22 | publisher = Universidad Veracruzana | accessdate = 2016-06-09 | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110220102041/http://www.uv.mx/eventos/inundaciones2005/PDF/20_%20RIESGO.pdf | url = http://www.uv.mx/eventos/inundaciones2005/PDF/20_%20RIESGO.pdf | archivedate = 2011-02-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。但是，大西洋飓风最佳路径数据库内没有把这一天气系统列为热带低气压<ref name="HURDAT" />。

